'''智慧電網'''（{{lang-en|smart grid}}、{{lang|en|smart electric grid}}、或{{lang|en|intelligent grid}}），一種現代化的[[輸電網路|輸電網路]]。利用[[信息及通信技术|信息及通信技术]]，以數位或類比<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pnl.gov/main/publications/external/technical_reports/PNNL-17167.pdf | title = Pacific Northwest GridWise™ Testbed Demonstration Projects, Part I. Olympic Peninsula Project | accessdate = 2014-01-15 | author = D. J. Hammerstrom et al. | archive-date = 2014-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140327053641/http://www.pnl.gov/main/publications/external/technical_reports/PNNL-17167.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>訊號偵測與收集供應端的電力供應狀況，與使用端的電力使用狀況。再用這些資訊來調整[[電力|電力]]的生產與輸配，或調整[[家電|家電]]及企業用戶的耗電量，以此达到节约能源、降低损耗、增强电网可靠性的目的。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://energy.gov/oe/technology-development/smart-grid | title = Smart Grid / Department of Energy | accessdate = 2012-06-18 | author = U.S. Department of Energy | archive-date = 2012-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120615130930/http://energy.gov/oe/technology-development/smart-grid | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。智能电网雛型是20世纪产生，是由一些中心发电机向大量用户传输电能的电网的简单升级。在传统电网的基础上，电能的传输[[拓扑|拓扑]]网络更加优化以满足更大范围的各种用电状况，如在用电量低的时段给[[电池|电池]]充电，然后在高峰时反过来给电网提供电能<ref>{{cite journal |author1=J. Hu |coauthors=A.Lanzon |title=Distributed finite-time consensus control for heterogeneous battery energy storage systems in droop-controlled microgrids |journal=IEEE Transactions on Smart Grid |date=2019 |volume=10 |issue=5 |page=4751-4761 |doi=10.1109/TSG.2018.2868112 |url=https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8452969 |access-date=2020-03-20 |archive-date=2020-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320150259/https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8452969 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

